{"tid":1039222,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[怨Daddy]曼聯傷10件 蘇B暗示關摩佬事","createTime":"2019-02-27T09:19:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-27T15:22:30.000Z","uid":31626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4f53daa09d3488e5711f11e8d8b62c85f6dd6646","tid":1039222,"uid":31626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T09:19:53.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=7eOXcRQmrlFTo7mkgo38hFuXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=4836939e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】曼聯於周三聯賽前出現10名傷兵，領隊蘇斯克查暗示前任領隊摩連奴責無旁貸。<br />\n<br />\n紅魔曼聯在周三聯賽對水晶宮，目前球隊有包括拉舒福特、安東尼馬迪爾、連格、菲爾鍾斯等10名球員受傷，領隊蘇斯克查（Ole Gunnar Solskjaers）暗示與前任領隊摩連奴有關。<a href=\"http://根據goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E6%A0%B9%E6%93%9Agoal.com&d=7eOXcRQmrlFTo7mkgo38hFuXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=58544888\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">根據goal.com</a>分析指，曼聯在摩佬領軍下，場均衝刺是98次，蘇B領軍後卻達108.6次，這是導致球員受傷的其中一個原因。<br />\n<br />\n「我是否要等到季初才要求球員改變打法？還是馬上要他們加強壓迫對手？大家都看到我的選擇，我要求大家打出曼聯的足球，如果你要成為球隊的一份子，就要確保自己有足夠狀態。」蘇斯克查說。言下之意，莫非是指過去曼聯球員狀態不足，暗示之前欠積極、太Hea，到他接手才突然加強壓迫力，球員容易受傷？<br />\n<br />\n記得摩佬上任之初就説過：「我的球員很少受傷！」紅魔在2016/17年球季的奔跑距離是4023公里，排英超末席；2017/18年球季稍稍增至4099公里，仍然排聯賽倒數第2。這在現代足球勁旅而言，實在是不合格。"},{"pid":"54ab822b88b4f8dbc0c291d00f8b0cffcd86ec54","tid":1039222,"uid":31626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T09:21:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eb8a7a28a5f662931d4b554fb77950404e2668b","tid":1039222,"uid":3342,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T09:35:57.000Z","msg":"最衰都係死利狗"},{"pid":"a878e9bf9d740267bd00db47675beedc5e6f25c6","tid":1039222,"uid":8636,"like":7,"dislike":5,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T10:38:35.000Z","msg":"作者自己谷精上腦亂刷FF都有得屈落蘇斯克查度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個作者同反曼狗攬撚住死全家就最撚好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bed55f560df7fcec16881852f3f1686cdc0412e","tid":1039222,"uid":31626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T15:18:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4180e99851b20cd1aa3ce82898b2f3fded4a68e7","tid":1039222,"uid":195009,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"4eb8a7a28a5f662931d4b554fb77950404e2668b","tid":1039222,"uid":3342,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T09:35:57.000Z","msg":"最衰都係死利狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T15:22:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0fDR7Qt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0fDR7Qt.png&h=f9484685&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}